{"id":307833,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/主场新闻-新华社三级片截图当「美国死刑实录」/","date":"2013-08-07T05:09:24Z","modified":"2013-08-07T05:09:24Z","title":"主场新闻 | 新华社三级片截图当「美国死刑实录」","content":"<p>新华社及《环球时报》又闹笑话：日前，《环球时报》网站以「女囚死刑实录 揭世界最黑暗一面」为题，刊出一辑照片，内为一个穿着性感的女子被绑在手术床上挣扎的情形，新华社等多家大陆媒体转载。网站Shanghaiist发现，这辑图片并非什么死刑实录，而是外国一部色情电影的截图。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/assss_v60wc_600x0.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-307835\" alt=\"assss_v60wc_600x0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/assss_v60wc_600x0.png\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/assss_v60wc_600x0.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/assss_v60wc_600x0-300x188.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>新华社图片频道的官方微博在介绍图辑时，还强调「这不是电影」：</p>\n<blockquote><p>【女囚死刑实录 揭世界最黑暗一面】#胆小勿入#这不是电影！这是美国一监狱医疗人员实录一女死囚执刑全过程；犯人是个很年轻的女孩，贩毒罪名……「我插着手冷冷看着她，今天就是她的行刑日」……</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Xinhua_7yJUC_600x0.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-307836\" alt=\"Xinhua_7yJUC_600x0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Xinhua_7yJUC_600x0.png\" width=\"549\" height=\"232\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Xinhua_7yJUC_600x0.png 549w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Xinhua_7yJUC_600x0-300x126.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 549px) 100vw, 549px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">Shanghaiist指出，这辑照片是色情电影Lethal Injection（《致命注射》）截图。但图辑已被多家大陆媒体当作新闻转载。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/123456789_gHeAu_600x0.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-307837\" alt=\"123456789_gHeAu_600x0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/123456789_gHeAu_600x0.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/123456789_gHeAu_600x0.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/123456789_gHeAu_600x0-300x189.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/asdsddd_Adx2B_600x0.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-307838\" alt=\"asdsddd_Adx2B_600x0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/asdsddd_Adx2B_600x0.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"443\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/asdsddd_Adx2B_600x0.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/asdsddd_Adx2B_600x0-300x221.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/dasd_UBLQB_600x0.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-307839\" alt=\"dasd_UBLQB_600x0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/dasd_UBLQB_600x0.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/dasd_UBLQB_600x0.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/dasd_UBLQB_600x0-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>主场新闻于一色情网站发现关于Lethal Injection（《致命注射》）的影片宣传介绍。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Screen20Shot202013-08-0720at2011.26.2120AM_cdAPn_600x0.png\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-307840\" alt=\"Screen20Shot202013-08-0720at2011.26.2120AM_cdAPn_600x0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Screen20Shot202013-08-0720at2011.26.2120AM_cdAPn_600x0.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Screen20Shot202013-08-0720at2011.26.2120AM_cdAPn_600x0.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/Screen20Shot202013-08-0720at2011.26.2120AM_cdAPn_600x0-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,20534],"tags":[9540,10702,8816,12134]}